| Status | Color | Description |
|--------|-------|-------------|
| ğŸŸ¢ Running | Soft Green | Job is actively running |
| ğŸŸ¡ Pending | Soft Orange | Job is waiting in queue |
| ğŸ”µ Completed | Soft Blue | Job finished successfully |
